-- 3M says settles patent suit with Batteries.com
-- 
-- Thu Jul 5, 2007 12:00pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/07/05/us-threem-lawsuit-idUSWNAS534020070705

 

 (Reuters) - Diversified manufacturer 3M Co. ( MMM.N ) said Batteries.com acknowledged infringement of 3M's patent rights to lithium ion battery technology and agreed to discontinue sale of the infringing products. 

 Remaining terms of the settlement were confidential, 3M, which had filed a patent infringement suit against Batteries.com, said. (Reporting by Sweta Singh in Bangalore)